# Config Conventions

## Structure
- `path.base_dir`: `/data0/djx/EMDiffuse/experiments`
- `datasets.train.which_dataset.name`: `["data.sr_dataset", "SuperResolutionDataset"]`
- `model.which_networks[0].args.unet.in_channel`: always 2 (cond + noisy)
- `model.which_networks[0].args.unet.out_channel`: always 1

## Creating New Configs
- Copy from `WF2Density.json` as template
- Update `name`, dataset paths, and `task` field
- `task` should be `"super_resolution"` for our pipeline
- Use `//` for comments (stripped by parser in `core/praser.py`)

## Key Parameters
- `inner_channel`: 64 for 5090 GPUs (32 for smaller GPUs)
- `beta_schedule.train.n_timestep`: 2000
- `beta_schedule.test.n_timestep`: 1000
- `train.save_checkpoint_epoch`: checkpoint saving frequency (in epochs)
- `train.max_val_images`: max images logged to TensorBoard during validation (default 4)
- `train.val_gpu`: GPU index for async validation (null = sync on training GPU)
